  <original-body>Before (in a functional test):

@@@ ruby
def test_something
  # artist_url(:id =&gt; 1) # Errors&#8230;
  get :edit, :id =&gt; 1
  artist_url(:id =&gt; 1) # Now it works.
end
@@@

So with this patch the route will work before the request.</original-body>
